{"TopicId":65218,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Fly multiple planes at once","CreatedByName":"pjesapjes","CreatedById":17690,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-03-08T21:39:29Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"pjesapjes","CreatedById":17690,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-03-08T21:39:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHow many planes can you fly at once and safely land them somewhere few km away?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eand how close can you fly them.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERules:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E1. No gravity hack\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E2. No mechjeb\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E3. Just stock parts\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E4. No cheats at all\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E5. part clipping allowed.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Epost pictures or videos. videos would be awesome.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Epictures of fails and crashes also well accepted \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Emy first try with two planes went well.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote lang=\u0022en\u0022\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022//imgur.com/a/jtZC4\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EJavascript is disabled. View full album\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mareczex333","CreatedById":77858,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-03-08T21:47:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHmmm... my F-35s are easy to control \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E I think I could make 4 of them fly (for example to Island base) the only problem would be with landing \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pjesapjes","CreatedById":17690,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-03-08T21:53:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mareczex333\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Mareczex333\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHmmm... my F-35s are easy to control \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E I think I could make 4 of them fly (for example to Island base) the only problem would be with landing \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eyeah, they are super ! love your designs! keep up the GREAT work \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EDo the challenge and post the results if you have time \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E cheers.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Destroyer","CreatedById":36109,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-03-08T22:16:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHow do you switch in mid air? Won\u0027t it say \u0022cannot switch vessls under acceleration\u0022 or something?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pjesapjes","CreatedById":17690,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-03-08T22:22:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Destroyer\u0022 data-cite=\u0022The Destroyer\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHow do you switch in mid air? Won\u0027t it say \u0022cannot switch vessls under acceleration\u0022 or something?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ei thought so too. but surprisingly it does not. you can switch as long as the distance is under 2 km between the vessels i think.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Parallax","CreatedById":104180,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-03-08T22:22:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Eif my planes didn\u0027t disappear after a certain distance I could totally control two at once\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mareczex333","CreatedById":77858,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-03-08T22:31:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHahah \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E I brought 4 to the island and 2 crashed ;d I\u0027ll try again \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Parallax\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Parallax\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Eif my planes didn\u0027t disappear after a certain distance I could totally control two at once\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThat is a challange ;D to not make them dissappear and controll them ;d\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222014-03-09T17:23:44Z\u0022 title=\u002203/09/2014 05:23  PM\u0022 data-short=\u002210 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 9, 2014\u003C/time\u003E by Mareczex333\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Hodo","CreatedById":78218,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-03-08T22:37:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Parallax\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Parallax\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Eif my planes didn\u0027t disappear after a certain distance I could totally control two at once\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EStay with in 2.59km and they will not disappear.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mareczex333","CreatedById":77858,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-03-09T01:19:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHere\u0027s my challenge:\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 conten