a","CreatedById":70823,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-02T23:34:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mareczex333\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Mareczex333\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHere\u0027s my challenge:\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/3S5qVDlqUXM?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt was my 3rd try \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E (2 firsts ended with 2 crashes at runway on island)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAs you see I don\u0027t have much problem with landing. I was just too stupid to land on top of tower \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI can try again and land them all. Bigger number of planes is problem not because it\u0027s hard to control, but because my PC would melt ;d\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EJebediah Kerman is so badass he tries to land on the tower\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Aphobius","CreatedById":79391,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-04T00:40:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI can also fly two at once. But I don\u0027t know if that landing qualifies me for this challenge.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.twitch.tv/aphobius/c/3947122\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EVideo\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JTG","CreatedById":106203,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-16T23:51:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mareczex333\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Mareczex333\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHere\u0027s my challenge:\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/3S5qVDlqUXM?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt was my 3rd try \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E (2 firsts ended with 2 crashes at runway on island)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAs you see I don\u0027t have much problem with landing. I was just too stupid to land on top of tower \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI can try again and land them all. Bigger number of planes is problem not because it\u0027s hard to control, but because my PC would melt ;d\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWow, that has to be pretty tedious, trying to keep them all on a good flight.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI must ask, where did you get those colored parts?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"B11267","CreatedById":83641,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-21T06:42:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022pjesapjes\u0022 data-cite=\u0022pjesapjes\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cp\u003E1. No gravity hack\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E4. No cheats at all\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E5. part clipping allowed.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENo cheats at all? That would mean rule 1 is redundant. And rule 5 is contradictory. WHY U NO PROPER RULE?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ephraim","CreatedById":168722,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-14T17:54:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMan please how do you spawn planes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Slam_Jones","CreatedById":125101,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-14T18:43:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222756408\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002265218\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221473875667\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022168722\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ephraim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n53 minutes ago, ephraim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMan please how do you spawn planes\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpawn one from Runway, move it off the runway onto the grass nearby.\u00A0 Go back and spawn another one, move it also off the runway.\u00A0 Rinse and repeat as needed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-----\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI use tons of mods otherwise I\u0027d give it a shot.\u00A0 Here\u0027s what my tactic would have been:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- Make a simple, slow, easy-to-glide plane.\u00A0 Simple enough that I can put the throttle to full and it will automatically take off and level out, which will not go faster than perhaps 50m/s.\u00A0 Slower is better.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- Make sure each has a parachute or two attached, enough for a safe landing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- Line up 3, 4, 5, or however many I can manage on the grass beside the runway.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- Fly them in formation, then cut the engines off, one after another, just before/above the island, and deploy parachutes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- Watch as they gracefully land next to each other.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n- Profit!!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-09-14T18:48:28Z\u0022 title=\u002209/14/2016 06:48  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003ESeptember 14, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Slam_Jones\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-09-15T03:38:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow that the question is answered, the thread will be closed, since it\u0027s been inactive for over 2 years.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}